  "text": "We briefly explain the idea of codebook-based beamformer quantization. We also review phase shift keying (PSK) & quadrature amplitude modulation (QAM)-singular vector quantization (SVQ) in [CITATION_1] and their complexities before describing the proposed NTCQ.",
